{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AHueLC7t8oNcaFYQe7zYsM","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→## Codebase Patterns\n     2→- Project uses Vite + vanilla TypeScript (no framework)\n     3→- PIXI.js v8 for canvas rendering — use `new Application()` then `await app.init(...)` pattern\n     4→- Source code lives in `src/`\n     5→- npm is the package manager (no bun/pnpm)\n     6→- TypeScript strict mode enabled with `noUnusedLocals` and `noUnusedParameters`\n     7→- Run `npx tsc --noEmit` for typecheck, `npx vite build` for build\n     8→- Canvas is full-viewport with `resizeTo: window`, background `#1a1a2e`\n     9→\n    10→---\n    11→\n    12→## 2026-03-02 - US-001\n    13→- Set up Vite + TypeScript project scaffold\n    14→- Installed PIXI.js v8 and created full-viewport responsive canvas\n    15→- Canvas uses `resizeTo: window`, `autoDensity: true`, and `devicePixelRatio` for crisp mobile rendering\n    16→- Added `index.html` with viewport meta (no scaling), CSS reset for full-screen canvas\n    17→- Files changed: `package.json`, `tsconfig.json`, `index.html`, `src/main.ts`, `.gitignore`\n    18→- **Learnings for future iterations:**\n    19→  - Vite `create` won't scaffold into a non-empty directory — set up manually instead\n    20→  - PIXI.js v8 uses async init pattern: `const app = new Application(); await app.init({...})`\n    21→  - `autoDensity: true` + `resolution: devicePixelRatio` ensures sharp rendering on high-DPI phone screens\n    22→  - The viewport meta tag needs `maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no` to prevent pinch-zoom on mobile\n    23→---\n    24→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6cbc2844-863a-4a04-96e0-be307e309c99","uuid":"c775bf0e-5476-4290-90da-b6596a7e2180","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/jstoone/Sites/linjer/.chief/prds/main/progress.md","content":"## Codebase Patterns\n- Project uses Vite + vanilla TypeScript (no framework)\n- PIXI.js v8 for canvas rendering — use `new Application()` then `await app.init(...)` pattern\n- Source code lives in `src/`\n- npm is the package manager (no bun/pnpm)\n- TypeScript strict mode enabled with `noUnusedLocals` and `noUnusedParameters`\n- Run `npx tsc --noEmit` for typecheck, `npx vite build` for build\n- Canvas is full-viewport with `resizeTo: window`, background `#1a1a2e`\n\n---\n\n## 2026-03-02 - US-001\n- Set up Vite + TypeScript project scaffold\n- Installed PIXI.js v8 and created full-viewport responsive canvas\n- Canvas uses `resizeTo: window`, `autoDensity: true`, and `devicePixelRatio` for crisp mobile rendering\n- Added `index.html` with viewport meta (no scaling), CSS reset for full-screen canvas\n- Files changed: `package.json`, `tsconfig.json`, `index.html`, `src/main.ts`, `.gitignore`\n- **Learnings for future iterations:**\n  - Vite `create` won't scaffold into a non-empty directory — set up manually instead\n  - PIXI.js v8 uses async init pattern: `const app = new Application(); await app.init({...})`\n  - `autoDensity: true` + `resolution: devicePixelRatio` ensures sharp rendering on high-DPI phone screens\n  - The viewport meta tag needs `maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no` to prevent pinch-zoom on mobile\n---\n","numLines":24,"startLine":1,"totalLines":24}}}
