{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_017TKVbVboDWoTSEyFHuYkra","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**US-003 complete.** Here's what was implemented:\n\n- **`src/connections.ts`** — New module with drag-to-connect logic:\n  - Pointer event handling: `pointerdown` on boxes starts drag, `pointermove` draws preview, `pointerup` commits or discards\n  - Preview line (green, semi-transparent bezier curve) follows finger during drag\n  - Committed connections rendered as quadratic bezier curves with perpendicular offset for gentle arcs\n  - Arrowheads at target box edge indicate direction\n  - Lines connect edge-to-edge (ray-box intersection) for clean visuals\n  - Hit testing on pointer release to determine target box\n  - Exports `ConnectionManager` with `connections` array and `redraw()` for future stories\n- **`src/main.ts`** — Updated to capture `createGrid` return value and pass it to `setupConnections`\n- **`index.html`** — Added `touch-action: none` to canvas CSS for reliable mobile drag handling\n\nThere are still stories with `passes: false` remaining (US-004 through US-012)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":248,"cache_read_input_tokens":60944,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":248},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a8cef887-0087-4d9f-a08c-41c7810edf4e","uuid":"8d6da3c0-3040-4b47-b23f-6ed076f45d6b"}
